  "section": "2.1: Quests and combat, unlock Miscellania",
  "stepText": "If you have (at least) two grown teak trees on Fossil Island, use the butler method to chop and make 1175 teak planks (example video of 2 tick teaks with butler plankmake: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GA987x97AKQ) using digsite pendants instead of a mounted digsite and dueling rings to bank for more necklaces and/or run energy as necessary (alternatively you can grab a necklace from the museum camp bank chest on Fossil Island after it breaks). Note that you have to take the long way (east) instead of the shortcut to the trees.\n",
